Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Vigilance
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=The Weapon of Invocation
By: Ibn 'Arabi
Glossary:
  - Term: dhikr
    Definition: Invocation, remembrance (of God).
---
When the novices forget their dhikr for one breath, then Satan is with
them, for Satan spies upon them. So when forgetfulness enters the
heart, then he enters, but when the dhikr enters certainly he will
depart.
